      <div class="msgContentFrame">All spells cast by a THM are frontal AEO cone. Your range is quite far, but only party members in a cone in front of you will be cured. It doesn't matter if you are casting Sacrifice or Cure or Stoneskin. THM is frontal cone only. Same goes for all attack spells. Spells cast as a CON are AOE circular around the target. The AOE circle doesn't extend as far distance-wise as the THM cone.</div>
